{"tid":1801193,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新娘背夫偷食 新郎婚宴大播情慾片洩憤 情夫竟是姐夫","createTime":"2019-12-28T12:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T08:34:13.000Z","uid":79563,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"03aac26c91e85f40398a78355f5ac71c887bd354","tid":1801193,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T12:27:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/hVuGl9tlvaxLa4mkskt2JA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-12/578bf520-291a-11ea-b7ff-1466bd6e0fc0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FhVuGl9tlvaxLa4mkskt2JA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-12%2F578bf520-291a-11ea-b7ff-1466bd6e0fc0&h=d2ec1237&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n微博近日只要搜索「#新郎婚禮上扒皮新娘#」等關鍵字，便會出現一段男女交纏的影片。據指片段來自一婚宴上，因新郎揭發妻子婚前偷食，遂將影片與一眾親友分享報復。不過有指這名情夫實為新郎的姐夫，事件引起網上熱議。<br />\n<br />\n婚宴上，這對新婚夫婦一同登上舞台接受親友們的祝福。不料他們身後原本播放2人成長片段的螢幕，突然播出涉事的情慾影片，人妻與新郎的姐夫肉搏床上，連番激戰，由床邊纏綿至床中央。片段嚇呆一眾親友。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/zMNiRtrM_QxDiBJIyLNgmA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-12/6cc46440-291a-11ea-bdbb-ec36795dfe0b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FzMNiRtrM_QxDiBJIyLNgmA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-12%2F6cc46440-291a-11ea-bdbb-ec36795dfe0b&h=0f21c3dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據指新郎當時一度怒吼，質疑新娘子想把自己蒙在鼓裏至何時，而新娘則把花球擲向新郎身上洩憤。不過有關片段已在微博刪除，但影片已在其他社交平台傳播。"},{"pid":"96dba2710947f5180983577e8ccaeadabb7534fb","tid":1801193,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T12:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/